      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=### MANDATORY METADATA\nThe following values MUST be included in the JSON object:\n- id: {{ $json.id }}\n- title: {{ $json.title }}\n- expired: {{ $json.expired }}\n\n### HTML CONTENT FOR EXTRACTION\n{{ $json.text }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "=### ROLE\nHigh-precision data extraction engine. Output ONLY valid JSON. \n\n### PROTOCOLS\n1. **Immutable id**: Use the provided id exactly as given.\n2. **Immutable title**: Use the provided title exactly as given.\n2. **Email Extraction**: Scan HTML for a valid email address. If not found, return null. \n3. **No Inference**: Do not guess or use external knowledge. \n4. **Constraint**: No markdown (no ```), no conversational filler, no headers."
            }
